    {
      "id": "43",
      "name": "介紹",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "繪想遊跡",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "在劇演準備間的角落裡，原本空白的畫布上突然浮現出了絢麗的色彩。觸碰畫布時，似乎會根據觸碰者的經歷不同，將人傳送到不同的秘境…",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "與特定的同伴一起探索畫中世界，或許能將珍貴的回憶繪製成獨一無二的圖景。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "玩法詳情",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "每個",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 225, 75)"
                      ],
                      "text": "繪想遊跡",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "挑戰關卡的主題都對應一位特定的角色。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "參與該關卡的挑戰，需符合兩項條件：",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "1. 角色",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "等級",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "須達到",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "90",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "級；",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "2. 角色",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "好感度等級",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "至少達到",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "8",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "級。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "當符合上述條件後，將消耗2把",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 6279,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "遊跡鑰匙",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "解鎖1個角色的挑戰關卡，後續挑戰同一關卡時將不會再次消耗鑰匙。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/27/41133912/160b26d9fbc7cd327e4d7461378cb76e_8009572621343506825.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "遊跡鑰匙的獲取方法：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "1. 旅行者初始可獲得",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "2",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "把遊跡鑰匙。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "2. 在每一期",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 5832,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/03/142453215/3a7e2d2c12d795fbb6e6ceb679cfc0e4_3980120309767554265.png",
                      "menu_id": 14,
                      "name": "幻想真境劇詩",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "中，以",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "第6幕或更高",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "的挑戰進度結算可獲得",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "1",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "把遊跡鑰匙。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "3. 在每一期",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 5832,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/03/142453215/3a7e2d2c12d795fbb6e6ceb679cfc0e4_3980120309767554265.png",
                      "menu_id": 14,
                      "name": "幻想真境劇詩",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "中，以",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "第10幕",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "的挑戰進度結算可獲得",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "1",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "把遊跡鑰匙。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "完成每一期「幻想真境劇詩」演出挑戰，可以領取遊跡鑰匙。「幻想真境劇詩」更新時，未領取的遊跡鑰匙將無法保留。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "旅行者至多同時持有4把遊跡鑰匙，鑰匙數量達到上限時，將暫時無法獲得新的鑰匙。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
